        <description><span style="background-color:#CDFF7D;border-bottom:2px groove #000000;font-style:italic;">Submitter: Schulte-Schlagbaum AG</span><br/><br/><span style="text-decoration:underline; border-bottom: 1px solid #000;">Description</span><br/>  In this EEP family electronic locking systems and mortise locks are collected
